Due to the popularity of the first series of [[Talkin' 'Bout Your Generation]], a second series was commissioned and began airing on the 7th of February, 2010. The series aired for 10 episodes and took a three month break before continuing to air on the 1st of August, 2010. The series is set to run for a further 12 episodes totalling 22 for the second series.
